description: Those who control art control us. 1/4-note, 4/4, 4-chord music uses rhythmic ratios of 1 - allowing your brain to disengage listening. If we are used to disengaging our brains in our downtime, we'll be less equipped to use when we actually need to - get our answers handed, not thinking them through.
